Calculemos la base del tangente:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial X}{\partial\theta}\left(\theta,t\right)=\left(-\cosh t\sin\theta,\cosh t\cos\theta,0\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial X}{\partial t}\left(\theta,t\right)=\left(\sinh t\cos\theta,\sinh t\sin\theta,1\right)
\]

\end_inset

 por lo que obtenemos los coeficientes de la primera forma fundamental:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E=\cosh^{2}t,\ F=0,\ G=\cosh^{2}t
\]

\end_inset

 De modo que 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

 es una parametrización isoterma de 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

, y se verifica
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S\ minimal\iff\frac{\partial^{2}X}{\partial\theta^{2}}+\frac{\partial^{2}X}{\partial t^{2}}=0\iff\left(-\cosh t\cos\theta,-\cosh t\sin\theta,0\right)+\left(\cosh t\cos\theta,\cosh t\sin\theta,0\right)=0\checkmark
\]

\end_inset

 Y vemos que 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 es minimal.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Ahora, como 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 es minimal, entonces 
\begin_inset Formula $H\equiv0$
\end_inset

, y las curvaturas principales son 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}=-\lambda_{2}$
\end_inset

.
 De esta forma, un punto será umbilical si, y solo si, 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}=\lambda_{2}=0$
\end_inset

, si, y solo si, 
\begin_inset Formula $K\equiv0$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Calculemos, entonces 
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

 (como la parametrización es isoterma, en particular es ortogonal):
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
K=\frac{-1}{2\sqrt{EG}}\left[\left(\frac{E_{t}}{\sqrt{EG}}\right)_{t}+\left(\frac{G_{\theta}}{\sqrt{EG}}\right)_{\theta}\right]=-\frac{1}{2\cdot\cosh^{2}t}\left[\left(\frac{2\cosh t\sinh t}{\cosh^{2}t}\right)_{t}+\left(\frac{0}{\cosh^{2}t}\right)_{\theta}\right]=-\frac{1}{2\cosh^{2}t}\cdot\left(\frac{2\sinh t}{\cosh t}\right)=
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
=-\frac{1}{\cosh^{2}t}\frac{\cosh^{2}t-\sinh^{2}t}{\cosh^{2}t}=-\frac{1}{\cosh^{4}t}\neq0
\]

\end_inset

 Y no hay puntos umbilicales.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

